(454, 6, NULL, 'ID.GV', 'Governance', 'The policies, procedures, and processes to manage and monitor the organizations regulatory, legal, risk, environmental, and operational requirements are understood and inform the management of cybersecurity risk.', '2021-11-26 10:46:01', '2021-11-26 10:46:01'),
