(474, 6, NULL, 'ID.SC-4', 'Supply Chain Management', 'Suppliers and 3rd-party partners are routinely assessed to confirm that they are meeting their contractual obligations. Reviews of audits, summaries of test results, or other equivalent evaluations of suppliers/providers are conducted', '2021-11-26 10:46:01', '2021-11-26 10:46:01'),
